cu.explanation_en: Setting the RRC log level to an invalid value 'invalid' will cause the RRC logging module to fail initialization, preventing proper radio resource control logging and potentially masking critical connection issues.

du.explanation_en: Setting the RF simulator model name to an invalid value 'invalid' will cause the simulator to fail loading, leading to radio frequency simulation errors and disrupted signal processing.
du.explanation_zh: 將 RF 模擬器模型名稱設定為無效值 'invalid' 會導致模擬器載入失敗，造成無線電頻率模擬錯誤並中斷訊號處理。
